- Will you grab a robot?

545
00:17:44,172 --> 00:17:45,331
I'll bring a card.

546
00:17:45,332 --> 00:17:47,172
- I'll try to find a robot.
- Okay.

547
00:17:47,602 --> 00:17:48,771
We're at an advantage here.

548
00:17:48,772 --> 00:17:50,211
