549
00:17:50,212 --> 00:17:51,842
- You can't bring a car, right?
- What?

550
00:17:52,112 --> 00:17:53,171
We can go, "Dad's car."

551
00:17:53,172 --> 00:17:54,341
(Team Jong Min's initials)

552
