563
00:18:16,802 --> 00:18:17,901
- Chair.
- What?

564
00:18:17,902 --> 00:18:19,571
Chair.

565
00:18:19,572 --> 00:18:21,148
(Team Se Yoon gets 2 cards as soon as the round begins.)

566
00:18:21,172 --> 00:18:24,942
(Team Jong Min's initials, Team Se Yoon's initials)

567
00:18:25,572 --> 00:18:27,182
Let's go, Jong Min!

568
00:18:28,982 --> 00:18:31,552
(Joon said he would look for a robot.)

569
00:18:34,122 --> 00:18:35,181
Robot.

570
00:18:35,182 --> 00:18:36,452
