(In standard Korean, it's "robot," not "robotte.")

578
00:18:51,272 --> 00:18:52,631
- Card.
- They took our cards with a robot.

579
00:18:52,632 --> 00:18:54,032
- Rieul, bieup, and tiguet.
- Card.

580
00:18:54,342 --> 00:18:55,572
King.

581
