If you say it like that, it will ruin your public image.

586
00:19:05,112 --> 00:19:07,822
(Team Jong Min's initials, Team Se Yoon's initials)

587
00:19:08,552 --> 00:19:09,821
The card reader.

588
00:19:09,822 --> 00:19:11,552
(Team Se Yoon only has 3 cards left.)

589
