596
00:19:26,732 --> 00:19:28,741
I'm thirsty. Let me get some water. Hurry up.

597
00:19:28,742 --> 00:19:30,022
- I don't have any water.
- I...

598
00:19:30,842 --> 00:19:32,811
(Why is he suddenly asking for water?)

599
00:19:32,812 --> 00:19:36,011
Come here. Hurry.

600
00:19:36,012 --> 00:19:37,482
- Hurry up. Come here.
- What?

601
00:19:39,082 --> 00:19:40,881
- Water slap.
- Water slap.

602
00:19:40,882 --> 00:19:42,382
Hurry up. Come here.

603
00:19:43,152 --> 00:19:45,722
(Water slap: Mieum, ssangdigeut, giyeok)

604
00:19:46,752 --> 00:19:47,761
- Water slap.
- Water slap.

605
00:19:47,762 --> 00:19:48,891
