- Water slap.

606
00:19:48,892 --> 00:19:50,021
(All three initials are there.)

607
00:19:50,022 --> 00:19:51,132
Water slap.

608
00:19:52,032 --> 00:19:53,831
(Rieul, bieup, tiguet, kieuk, ssanggiyeok, pieup, digeut...)

609
00:19:53,832 --> 00:19:55,602
Rice cooker.

610
00:19:56,362 --> 00:19:58,402
Great.

611
00:19:59,202 --> 00:20:01,642
