613
00:20:04,772 --> 00:20:07,742
(They're tied at 8 cards.)

614
00:20:08,012 --> 00:20:09,441
Joon, just bring something.

615
00:20:09,442 --> 00:20:10,962
We just have to grab something and go.

616
00:20:11,552 --> 00:20:14,122
Let me just grab one more. There.

617
00:20:14,882 --> 00:20:16,221
- Photo.
- It's neck and neck!

618
00:20:16,222 --> 00:20:17,651
- Photo.
- That counts.

619
00:20:17,652 --> 00:20:18,652
Photo.

620
00:20:18,652 --> 00:20:19,652
- Clock.
- Clock. Hurry.

621
00:20:19,653 --> 00:20:20,661
- We got that one?
- Clock.

622
00:20:20,662 --> 00:20:21,662
We did.

623
