You allowed "older brother" earlier.

624
00:20:22,922 --> 00:20:24,861
Five, four, three,

625
00:20:24,862 --> 00:20:26,892
- An older brother to a brother.
- two, one.

626
00:20:27,202 --> 00:20:28,661
- Stop!
- Okay.

627
00:20:28,662 --> 00:20:29,680
