628
00:20:29,731 --> 00:20:33,001
All right. Let's go over the scores for Round Two.

629
00:20:33,106 --> 00:20:34,575
- Team Jong Min stole...
- Okay.

630
00:20:34,576 --> 00:20:35,806
Seven cards.

631
00:20:36,206 --> 00:20:37,315
Team Se Yoon stole...

632
00:20:37,316 --> 00:20:38,815
- Nine cards.
- nine cards.

633
00:20:38,816 --> 00:20:39,845
- So...
- What?

634
00:20:39,846 --> 00:20:41,115
- Round Two...
- Okay.

635
00:20:41,116 --> 00:20:42,916
- Nice.
- goes to Team Se Yoon.

636
00:20:44,086 --> 00:20:46,455
Don't say we have to put everything back.

637
00:20:46,456 --> 00:20:47,586
This is killing me.

638
00:20:47,826 --> 00:20:50,256
- The current score is 1 to 1.
- Yes.

639
00:20:50,626 --> 00:20:51,795
For the last round,

640
00:20:51,796 --> 00:20:53,965
two members from each team will play.

641
00:20:53,966 --> 00:20:55,995
