642
00:20:55,996 --> 00:20:57,165
- Those two.
- Darn it.

643
00:20:57,166 --> 00:20:58,235
Okay.

644
00:20:58,236 --> 00:21:01,265
You must prepare yourselves for Round Three.

645
00:21:01,266 --> 00:21:02,266
