- All right.

647
00:21:04,036 --> 00:21:05,205
- Here it goes.
- Okay.

648
00:21:05,206 --> 00:21:06,436
- It will start soon.
- Okay.

649
00:21:06,546 --> 00:21:08,746
You must find an item with the same initials...

