656
00:21:22,256 --> 00:21:23,256
- What?
- Mieum, rieul...

657
00:21:23,257 --> 00:21:24,295
- What?
- Mieum, rieul, digeut, and ieung.

658
00:21:24,296 --> 00:21:25,625
(Mieum, rieul, digeut, and ieung)

659
00:21:25,626 --> 00:21:27,096
Mieum, rieul, digeut, and ieung.

660
00:21:27,326 --> 00:21:28,896
Gosh, this is hard.

661
00:21:29,936 --> 00:21:31,936
