663
00:21:35,236 --> 00:21:37,906
(grabs an item and starts running.)

664
00:21:38,706 --> 00:21:39,706
Does it...

665
00:21:40,746 --> 00:21:42,645
(Se Yoon.)

666
00:21:42,646 --> 00:21:44,276
