It's not wet. A dry bucket.

668
00:21:47,486 --> 00:21:48,685
- That makes sense.
- A dry bucket.

669
00:21:48,686 --> 00:21:50,185
- It works. A dry bucket.
- That totally works!

670
00:21:50,186 --> 00:21:52,255
For Round Three, the word has to match completely.

671
00:21:52,256 --> 00:21:53,855
- It does. A dry bucket.
- A dry bucket.

672
00:21:53,856 --> 00:21:55,225
- Seon Ho, just go.
- Is it wet?

673
00:21:55,226 --> 00:21:56,355
It's completely dry. A dry bucket.

674
00:21:56,356 --> 00:21:58,355
It has to match perfectly without any forced adjectives.

675
00:21:58,356 --> 00:21:59,796
You're so frustrating.

676
00:22:01,226 --> 00:22:02,586
- It must match completely.
- Hey.

677
00:22:02,796 --> 00:22:04,366
