688
00:22:29,526 --> 00:22:30,726
My head is hot.

689
00:22:31,456 --> 00:22:32,525
- No?
- No.

690
00:22:32,526 --> 00:22:33,795
- My head is hot.
- No.

691
00:22:33,796 --> 00:22:34,925
- Wrong.
- I have a heat rash.

692
