- Wrong.

698
00:22:44,436 --> 00:22:46,006
It's just one word.

699
00:22:48,446 --> 00:22:50,276
No. Seon Ho, keep going.

700
00:22:50,476 --> 00:22:52,246
They're so frustrating.

701
00:22:53,416 --> 00:22:54,615
(A melodica is here.)

702
00:22:54,616 --> 00:22:56,685
Gosh, the eraser was here. I put it here.

703
00:22:56,686 --> 00:22:58,886
(Jong Min was looking around.)

704
00:22:59,686 --> 00:23:01,825
- Mieum, rieul, digeut, and ieung.
- He said it was one word.

705
00:23:01,826 --> 00:23:03,186
(Correct answer: Melodica)

706
00:23:03,856 --> 00:23:06,526
(He spots a melodica.)

707
00:23:07,066 --> 00:23:10,466
(Did he just put it down?)

708
00:23:10,966 --> 00:23:14,535
(Melodica 1, Melodica 2)

709
00:23:14,536 --> 00:23:16,776
(Melodica)

710
00:23:17,036 --> 00:23:18,576
A dry bucket was good.

711
00:23:18,636 --> 00:23:22,046
(Seon Ho just walks past them too.)

712
00:23:23,346 --> 00:23:25,116
(They're completely lost.)

713
00:23:25,346 --> 00:23:28,815
(Melodica 1, Melodica 2)

714
00:23:28,816 --> 00:23:30,056
I don't see anything.

715
00:23:31,886 --> 00:23:32,916
He said no.

716
00:23:33,826 --> 00:23:34,855
Did you find it?

717
00:23:34,856 --> 00:23:36,425
