719
00:23:38,396 --> 00:23:39,596
This is it, right?

720
00:23:39,966 --> 00:23:41,165
Guess what it is.

721
00:23:41,166 --> 00:23:42,695
- All right.
- It's not Mirinda.

722
00:23:42,696 --> 00:23:44,035
It's not a dry bucket.

723
00:23:44,036 --> 00:23:45,096
It's a melodica.

724
00:23:45,236 --> 00:23:46,336
- Yes!
- Se Yoon.

725
00:23:46,766 --> 00:23:49,205
- Correct.
- Yes! It was a melodica.

726
00:23:49,206 --> 00:23:50,376
What's that?

727
00:23:50,476 --> 00:23:51,606
My knee hurts.

728
00:23:52,706 --> 00:23:54,205
Round Three goes to Team Se Yoon.

729
00:23:54,206 --> 00:23:55,245
- Okay.
- Nice.

730
00:23:55,246 --> 00:23:57,145
- Team Se Yoon won the mission.
- That was an easy one.

731
00:23:57,146 --> 00:23:59,145
- So they'll get ten time capsules.
- Okay!

732
00:23:59,146 --> 00:24:01,215
(Team Se Yoon obtains 10 time capsules.)

733
00:24:01,216 --> 00:24:02,285
We're off to a great start.

734
00:24:02,286 --> 00:24:03,632
- It was right for you to play.
- Yes.

735
00:24:03,656 --> 00:24:05,415
The bread here looked good.

736
00:24:05,416 --> 00:24:07,425
- I can smell bread. What's this?
- Gosh, it smells amazing.

737
00:24:07,426 --> 00:24:08,956
Hey, bread smells so good here.

738
00:24:09,086 --> 00:24:10,695
- Let's take a look at the bread.
- Buy us some bread!

739
00:24:10,696 --> 00:24:13,026
We came all the way here. We ought to have some bread.

740
00:24:13,256 --> 00:24:15,165
We should try some. They're baking it here.

741
00:24:15,166 --> 00:24:16,195
- Right.
- It smells so good.

742
00:24:16,196 --> 00:24:17,735
I saw them bake it here.

743
00:24:17,736 --> 00:24:20,336
