- What?

748
00:24:27,576 --> 00:24:29,605
- It's a lucky draw board.
- I know this game.

749
00:24:29,606 --> 00:24:30,616
No way.

750
00:24:30,716 --> 00:24:32,315
- You can play this.
- Yes.

751
00:24:32,316 --> 00:24:33,416
