757
00:24:45,526 --> 00:24:46,966
Ready or not, rock-paper-scissors.

758
00:24:47,266 --> 00:24:48,325
- Okay.
- Rock-paper-scissors.

759
00:24:48,326 --> 00:24:50,036
- Okay.
- One, two, three, four, and five.

760
00:24:50,436 --> 00:24:52,365
- I just need to beat one of them.
- A heart.

761
00:24:52,366 --> 00:24:53,536
